        "remediation": {
            "desc": "Enable **automatic head-branch deletion** after merges to minimize stale refs and confusion.\n- Enforce **least privilege** for branch creation\n- Apply **branch protection** and rulesets\n- Prefer short-lived feature branches with periodic pruning\n- Guard CI to avoid runs from obsolete branches",
            "references": [
